title: ICE / EGGHEAD barks tent
description: Things egghead says in the tent,

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Wild wild I wanna see -- where's t..."
dialogueTree.english: "Wild wild I wanna see -- where's the child I used to be!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Dziką dzicz zobaczyłbym – gdzie jest to dziecię, którym żem był!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Дзікую дзічыну ўбачыў бы — дзе тая дзіцятка, якой я быў!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Racketeer, disappear, surging thro..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Reketierze, dzikieś zwierzę! Pędzisz ostro w MEGA-sferze!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Рэкетыру, дзікая жывёла! Нясешся хутка ў МЕГА-сферы!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Die ganze Truppe fliegt mit Mach 3..."
dialogueTree.english: "Die ganze Truppe fliegt mit Mach 3 in den Himmel. Jaaa!!!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Die ganze Truppe fliegt mit Mach 3 in den Himmel. Jaaa!!!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Увесь атрад узлятае на неба з хуткасцю ў тры махі. Ды так!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Ziggy to the wiggy -- land of the..."
dialogueTree.english: "Ziggy to the wiggy -- land of the beautiful, children of sound!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Gibon na bidon – kraina piękna, dźwięku kolebka!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Гібон на бідон – край красы, калыска гукаў!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Bring it back to the source, subli..."
dialogueTree.english: "Bring it back to the source, subliminal force. No remorse."
dialogueTree.polish: „Powrót do źródła, do energii jutra. Wolności sutra”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Вяртанне да крыніцы, да энергіі заўтра. Сутра свабоды".

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""On the verge, beat submerged, dive..."
dialogueTree.english: "On the verge, beat submerged, divers converge!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Na krawędzi, bit ostry pędzi, głębię zwęzi!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "На краі, біт востры мчыць, глыбіню звузь!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Sandals make a man -- detour, ten-..."
dialogueTree.english: "Sandals make a man -- detour, ten-four, HARD CORE!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""All four, back door, HARD CORE!""
Egg Head: ""Stratosphere, canoneer, music seve..."
dialogueTree.english: "Stratosphere, canoneer, music severe -- you didn't mishear, this *IS* the premier!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Stratosfera, kanoniera, muza napiera – dobrze słyszycie, to *JEST* premiera!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Стратасфера, кананера, муза напірае – добра чуеце, гэта *ЁСЦЬ* прэм'ера!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Who conquers the floor? That was t..."
dialogueTree.english: "Who conquers the floor? That was then, this is chapter four!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Kto parkiet podbije? Było minęło, nowe serce bije!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Хто паркэт падбіе? Было мінула, новае сэрца б'е!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Wir sind schlecht, wir sind in Gef..."
dialogueTree.english: "Wir sind schlecht, wir sind in Gefahr, wir machen Pornos!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Wir sind schlecht, wir sind in Gefahr, wir machen Pornos!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Мы дрэнныя, мы ў небяспецы, мы робім порна!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Here we go, hyper-soul, inside --..."
dialogueTree.english: "Here we go, hyper-soul, inside -- into the MEGA-heart!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Lost and found, submerged in sound..."
dialogueTree.english: "Lost and found, submerged in sound, praying to the beat!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Biuro rzeczy znalezionych, w dźwięku zanurzonych, w bicie rozmodlonych!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Бюро знаходак, у гуку пагружаных, у біце замаленых!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Hate-gate, mate-date, no room for..."
dialogueTree.english: "Hate-gate, mate-date, no room for the fake-flake -- chicken-chaser night-cake!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Brama-drama, glejt-hejt, nie ma miejsca na fałsz-rausz – kurzy-pościg nocny-torcik!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Брама-драма, глейт-хейт, няма месца для фальш-раўш – курзі-пагоня начны-торцік!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Re-entry, here we go! Dance floor..."
dialogueTree.english: "Re-entry, here we go! Dance floor -- HARD CORE!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Ponowne wejście, dalej jazda! Dryg parkietowy – HARDKOROWY!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Зноў на сцэну, далей едзем! Рытм на поле – ЖОРСТКІ!"

dialogueTree.title: Egg Head: ""Solar heat, feel the beat -- one t..."
dialogueTree.english: "Solar heat, feel the beat -- one track, rhythm attack -- everybody ju-uuump!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Słoneczny żar, bitu dar – jedna ścieżka, od rytmu ciężka – wszyscy skaaaaczą!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Сонечны жар, біту дар – адна сцежка, ад рытму цяжкая – усе скааачуць!"
